In 2003, @kateashaw and I spent 5 months backpacking around South America. In Fortaleza, Brazil, at a very cool flea market, we bought a single seat hammock for, like, $10 USD or so. I schlepped itaround Brazil, strapped to my pack for weeks and weeks. And since 2003, we‚Äôve moved it from apartment to apartment to apartment to our house in Brooklyn. And now, 16 years later, it has a permanent spot. Never give up on your (somewhat eccentric and really quite modest) dreams!
